                  <locus n="1">1r-59r</locus>
                  <title xml:lang="bg">Служба за св. Иван Рилски за 19 октомври</title>
                  <author>anonymous</author>
                  <note>
                     <date type="churchCal" when="--10-19">19 October</date>
                  </note>
                  <filiation type="source">Other</filiation>
                  <filiation type="protograph"> Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <filiation type="antigraph"> Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <sampleText xml:lang="cu">
                     <head>М<seg rend="sup">с</seg>ца ѡктоврїа ѳ҃.і҃. дн҃ь. паметъ пр<seg rend="sup">д</seg>пбннаго ѡ҃ца начего иѡанна рылскаго пустынно жителю</head>
                     <incipit defective="false">
                Разума свѣтлости оукрашаетсе
              </incipit>
                     <explicit defective="false">
                
                оум<seg rend="sup">л</seg>и его ч<seg rend="sup">с</seg>таа да с<seg rend="sup">п</seg>сетъ дш҃е наше: славословїе велико. и ѿпу<seg rend="sup">с</seg>.
             </explicit>
                  </sampleText>
               </msItemStruct>
               <msItemStruct xml:id="ACD2" type="translation" defective="false">
                  <locus n="2">59r-102r</locus>
                  <title xml:lang="bg">Житие на св. Иван Рилски от Георги Скилица</title>
                  <author>George Skylitzes</author>
                  <note>The Greek original had not been not found yet. There are a plenty of unclear places in the Slavic translation.</note>
                  <filiation type="protograph">Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <filiation type="antigraph">Middle Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <filiation type="litRedaction">The text has only one redaction in the Slavic  tradition.</filiation>
                  <sampleText xml:lang="cu">
                     <head>Житие и жизнь пр<seg rend="sup">д</seg>пбнаго ѿца нашего иѡанна , просїав'шаго въ пустынны рылстѣи. и по въсе дн҃їѥ велика сътварающа чюдеса. съписано геѡргїемъ скилицѡ<seg rend="sup">м</seg>.</head>
                     <incipit defective="false">
                
                Сщ҃енное начети повѣданїе
              </incipit>
                     <explicit defective="false">
                
                слава и чьсть и покланꙗнїе <gap hand="ET"/>
                     </explicit>
                  </sampleText>
               </msItemStruct>
               <msItemStruct xml:id="ACD3" type="original" defective="false">
                  <locus n="3">102r-130r</locus>
                  <title xml:lang="bg">Рилско (народно, манастирско) житие на св. Иван Рилски</title>
                  <author>anonymous</author>
                  <note>The Life contains folklore legends and stories.</note>
                  <filiation type="source" subtype="other"> Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <filiation type="protograph"> Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <filiation type="antigraph"> Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <filiation type="litRedaction">Pre-Metaphrastic redaction</filiation>
                  <sampleText xml:lang="cu">
                     <head>Въ тьж<seg rend="sup">д</seg>е дн҃ь слово второе ст҃му иѡанну рылскому</head>
                     <incipit defective="false">
                
                Бысть чл҃кь д҃ховнь бл҃говѣрнь и хр<seg rend="sup">с</seg>толюбивь
              </incipit>
                     <explicit defective="false">
                
                блг<seg rend="sup">д</seg>тїю и чл҃колюбїемь Г҃а нашего їѵх Ха҃. ему же <gap hand="ET"/> вѣкомь. аминь.
             </explicit>
                  </sampleText>
               </msItemStruct>
               <msItemStruct xml:id="ACD4" type="original" defective="false">
                  <locus n="4">132r-185r</locus>
                  <title xml:lang="bg">Служба на св. Йоаким Осоговски (Сарандапорски)</title>
                  <author>anonymous</author>
                  <note>
                     <date type="churchCal" when="--08-01">1 August</date>
                  </note>
                  <filiation type="source" subtype="other"> Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <filiation type="protograph"> Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <filiation type="antigraph"> Bulgarian</filiation>
                  <sampleText xml:lang="cu">
                     <head>М<seg rend="sup">с</seg>ца авгус<seg rend="sup">т</seg>а зі҃. еже ѿ ѥдеса прѣнесенїе ст҃го оубруса и ст҃гом<seg rend="sup">ч</seg>ника диомида, и прп<seg rend="sup">д</seg>бнаго ѡц҃а нашего иѡакїма сарандапор'скаго</head>
                     <incipit defective="false">Испльнивь гн<seg rend="sup">с</seg>ѥ еѵ<seg rend="sup">г</seg>лїе прп<seg rend="sup">д</seg>обне
              </incipit>
                     <explicit defective="false">ꙗко мл҃ищи се ѡ дш҃ахь нш҃їи<seg rend="sup">х</seg>
                     </explicit>
                  </sampleText>
               </msItemStruct>
